      <title>李克强呼吁加大对毕业生就业支持</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-26/china-s-li-urges-stronger-employment-support-for-graduates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国国务院总理李强呼吁出台更多针对高校毕业生、农民工等重点群体的就业政策，以提振中国劳动力市场。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-26/china-s-li-urges-stronger-employment-support-for-graduates</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 12:33:22 GMT</pubDate>
