      <title>CFA 一级通过率升至 46%，再次高于历史平均水平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-26/cfa-level-i-pass-rate-rises-to-46-again-above-historic-average</link>
      <description><![CDATA[特许金融分析师考试第一级的通过率跃升至 46% ，高于历史平均水平——不过，已经推迟考试的考生的通过率要低得多。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-26/cfa-level-i-pass-rate-rises-to-46-again-above-historic-average</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 12:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
