      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-26/sri-lanka-official-creditors-agree-final-debt-restructure-deals</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据总统媒体部门报道，斯里兰卡与双边贷款机构官方债权人委员会就 58 亿美元的债务达成了最终重组协议。]]></description>
